<p>Yeah, what Sophos said… And if I were SCP-711, I might be a little pissed that I was imprisoned for 40~ years.</p>
<p>Also, it seems like a huge waste that the Foundation didn't identify the exact time and place of temporal displacement. With 40 years of warning, it would have been easy to get in there and set up some equipment to document and analyze the method by which it actually happened.</p>
