														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1511916">
									

<p>I used to have <a href="http://www.phonearena.com/phones/LG-RUMOR_id2281">one of these</a> - in 2007/8. CRAPPY display, but matches the specs.</p>
<p>As for the LCD/LED part - yea, except he's a dumb kid that has no idea how any of it works, so they called it something that was familiar to them. Plus there isn't a mention on how far back he went. Forty years? A full century? All we know is the word &quot;Negro&quot; was still in common use. Plus, did he age? Did he age <em>normally</em>? What did he OF?</p>
<p>He could have been thrown back to the days of Marconi, been unaging the entire time and just &quot;shut down&quot; when he reached the &quot;starting point.&quot;</p>
<p>Who knows?</p>

